bill.title: PRIDE Act of 2023 Promoting Respect for Individuals’ Dignity and Equality Act of 2023
bill.description: To permit legally married same-sex couples to amend their filing status for income tax returns outside the statute of limitations, to amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to clarify that all provisions shall apply to legally married same-sex couples in the same manner as other married couples, and for other purposes.

history.action: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
